nitrokey-hotp-verification
------------------------------------------
Nitrokey HOTP Verification Tool is a command line application, which
communicates with a HOTP USB Security Dongle (over HIDAPI/libusb or CCID) to
configure HOTP secrets and to verify HOTP codes. The Dongle being used needs to
support HOTP verification, which is - at the time of writing - supported by
Nitrokey Pro, Nitrokey Storage, Nitrokey 3 and Librem Key.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libhidapi0-0.8.0-rc1-1
  libusb1.0-1.0.21-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libhidapi-devel-0.8.0-rc1-1
  libusb1.0-devel-1.0.21-1
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/Nitrokey/nitrokey-hotp-verification

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/Nitrokey/nitrokey-hotp-verification/archive/refs/tags/v1.6.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack nitrokey-hotp-verification-1.6-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./nitrokey-hotp-verification-1.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/nitrokey-hotp-verification-1.6-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/nitrokey-hotp-verification-1.6-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(nitrokey-hotp-verification)
  /usr/bin/hotp_verification.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/nitrokey-hotp-verification.README
  /usr/share/doc/nitrokey-hotp-verification/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/nitrokey-hotp-verification/README.md

